{"word":"ἀταρβής","slug":"ἀταρβής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀταρβής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τάρβος'><el>τάρβος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>unfearing, fearless</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ἀτ. τῆς θέας</el> <i>having no fear about</i> the sight, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>causing no fear</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}